      "range": "3981-4035",
      "markText": "当富人越来越富的时候，千百万收入微薄的底层公民正掏空他们的储蓄，降低他们的购买力，为了投机而抵押他们的未来。",
      "totalCount": 154,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300145055&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3981&rangeEnd=4035",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bfb32ae0813ab9f29g015a46?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3981&rangeEnd=4035"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300145055_3_1164-1218",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1164-1218",
      "markText": "营销手段带来的压力，甚至怂恿人们购买双份的奢侈品——每间车库里两辆汽车——在消费市场上，已经显示出过度的征兆",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300145055&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1164&rangeEnd=1218",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bfb32ae0813ab9f29g015a46?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1164&rangeEnd=1218"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300145055_3_7694-7715",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "7694-7715",
      "markText": "美国经济的主要缺点不在于生产，而在于消费。",
      "totalCount": 84,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300145055&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=7694&rangeEnd=7715",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bfb32ae0813ab9f29g015a46?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=7694&rangeEnd=7715"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300145055_3_9100-9172",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "9100-9172",
      "markText": "当我们充分理解了20年代经济史的时候，我们将发现，终结了另一个繁荣时期的这场崩溃，其主要原因是：工业没能把它的进步（通过省力设备）传递给消费者。",
      "totalCount": 84,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300145055&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=9100&rangeEnd=9172",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bfb32ae0813ab9f29g015a46?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=9100&rangeEnd=9172"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300145055_3_721-805",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "721-805",
      "markText": "征服贫穷不再是一个遥不可及的幻想，“我们尚未达致目标，但我们有机会沿袭过去八年的政策，继续向前，在上帝的帮助下，我们很快就会看到，把贫穷从这个国家驱逐出去的日子就在前头",
      "totalCount": 80,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300145055&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=721&rangeEnd=805",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bfb32ae0813ab9f29g015a46?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=721&rangeEnd=805"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300145055_4_2263-2302",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2263-2302",
      "markText": "新车的购买量却像自由落体一样垂直下降，如今，开去年流行的车型不再是一件丢脸的事",
      "totalCount": 80,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300145055&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2263&rangeEnd=2302",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bfb32ae0813ab9f29g015a46?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2263&rangeEnd=2302"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300145055_3_9224-9267",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "9224-9267",
      "markText": "有人指控，他们的创造天才让机器取代了人。当然，创造发明在颠覆群体平衡上的作用并不新奇。",
      "totalCount": 75,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300145055&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=9224&rangeEnd=9267",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bfb32ae0813ab9f29g015a46?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=9224&rangeEnd=9267"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300145055_3_1651-1922",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1651-1922",
      "markText": "即使吃苦耐劳、集腋成裘的古训似乎已经被快速致富的捷径所取代。 ",
      "totalCount": 70,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300145055&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1651&rangeEnd=1922",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bfb32ae0813ab9f29g015a46?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1651&rangeEnd=1922"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300145055_3_8236-8267",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "8236-8267",
      "markText": "全国三分之二的储蓄是年收入超过10,000美元的家庭存下来的。",
      "totalCount": 70,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300145055&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=8236&rangeEnd=8267",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bfb32ae0813ab9f29g015a46?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=8236&rangeEnd=8267"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300145055_3_10644-10665",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "10644-10665",
      "markText": "怂恿工薪阶层以赊账的方式购买更多的奢侈品。",
      "totalCount": 68,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300145055&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=10644&rangeEnd=10665",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bfb32ae0813ab9f29g015a46?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=10644&rangeEnd=10665"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300145055_7_648-685",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "648-685",
      "markText": "一个简朴的国家塑造了杰斐逊的这样一个坚定信念：管得最少的政府便是最好的政府",
      "totalCount": 68,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300145055&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=648&rangeEnd=685",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bfb32ae0813ab9f29g015a46?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=648&rangeEnd=685"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300145055_3_3716-3778",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "3716-3778",
      "markText": "大部分的股票购买都是以保证金形式进行的，这意味着投资者包括那些现金不多但抱有很大期望的小投资者，仅支付了大约四分之一的价格。",
      "totalCount": 64,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300145055&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3716&rangeEnd=3778",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bfb32ae0813ab9f29g015a46?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3716&rangeEnd=3778"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300145055_12_1235-1290",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "1235-1290",
      "markText": "使这个问题不断恶化的是日渐缩小的家庭规模，这意味着，养活父母的重担如今落在了一两个孩子，而不是半打孩子的肩上。",
      "totalCount": 64,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300145055&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1235&rangeEnd=1290",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bfb32ae0813ab9f29g015a46?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1235&rangeEnd=1290"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300145055_3_8336-8361",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "8336-8361",
      "markText": "当一个人快要淹死的时候，未雨绸缪就显得不切实际了。",
      "totalCount": 56,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300145055&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=8336&rangeEnd=8361",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bfb32ae0813ab9f29g015a46?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=8336&rangeEnd=8361"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300145055_6_4911-4953",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "4911-4953",
      "markText": "面对新的处罚措施，那些藏钱的人开始拿出他们的黄金，来到存款的窗口，把黄金兑换成金券。",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300145055&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4911&rangeEnd=4953",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bfb32ae0813ab9f29g015a46?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4911&rangeEnd=4953"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300145055_6_12422-12493",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "12422-12493",
      "markText": "要归功于一家叫作“民用工程署”(CWA)的专门从事工作救济的部门的飞速发展，这个部门通过地区分部直接从华盛顿运作，因此避免了地方上的官样文章。",
      "totalCount": 52,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300145055&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=12422&rangeEnd=12493",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bfb32ae0813ab9f29g015a46?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=12422&rangeEnd=12493"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300145055_3_4111-4155",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "4111-4155",
      "markText": "几乎是不知不觉之间，经济控制中的一场变化发生了，从早期的产业资本主义转变为金融资本主义。",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300145055&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4111&rangeEnd=4155",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bfb32ae0813ab9f29g015a46?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4111&rangeEnd=4155"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300145055_4_7582-7608",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "7582-7608",
